Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a pirate alliance\Nwith Trafalgar Law{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and have come to Dressrosa\Nto hand Caesar over to Doflamingo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Luffy found out that the \Nprize for a fighting event
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwas the Flare-Flare Fruit, he decided to enter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Sanji found out that\NCaesar's hand-over was Doflamingo's trap and...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been totally deceived!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have only one purpose, Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Shaking Heaven and Earth!\NAdmiral Fujitora's Power!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:42.58,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,GREEN BIT - THE BEACH ON THE SOUTHEAST SIDE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joker! Kick this guy's ass already...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna hand him over to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't do anything that I asked you to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo! This deal is off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:05:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Wh-What're you talking about, you fool?!\NWe got this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how you talk to your boss\Nafter 10 years of silence?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him, Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NCaesar is one of my precious subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Issho-{\i1}san{\i0}, it's Caesar Clown who is with Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. He is the scientist from \Nthe poison gas incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if he is that Warlord's subordinate,\Nhe is not going to get charged.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll grant him amnesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Fujitora, appointed as a Navy admiral\Nthrough the World Military Draft.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear a lot about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say you're a monster who has \Nunquestionable power as well as Ryokugyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, why thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still new to the Navy so\Nit's hard for me to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,understand what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have enough evidence yet
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I have some information about
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you doing things that go against \Nthe rules of the Seven Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man right there was calling you "Joker" -\Nis that your nickname?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to investigate me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have to be really determined \Nand collect enough evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what's the Navy's decision\Nabout Law's punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding the news about you and\Nthe wanted pirates, the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you're allying with them as they say in the news,\Nyou're guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they have become your subordinates,\NLaw-{\i1}san{\i0}, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:06:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...not guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our mission depends on your response.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may have to arrest you and the Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, what kind of decision is that?!\NHe can just get away by lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My original plan failed completely.\NThe Navy is targeting us now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I lie now and try to \Ntake this matter to Dressrosa,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nit only makes it worse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to buy some time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats are not working under me!\NWe're allies as you read in the paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a clumsy man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we have to strip you of your title.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if the story ended there but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a meteorite?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-D-Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A meteorite is coming toward us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Issho-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What happened in that moment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only those three spots that they're standing\Nhave no damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Issho-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did the Fleet Admiral train you?!\NYou damn stray dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if he can see or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.\NI just wanted to test your skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.29,0:11:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'm going to arrest you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay, Law-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're thinking\Nyou can get away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:17.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,DRESSROSA - FRANKY AND THE OTHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Flower Field?!\NAre you gonna go on a picnic?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What about you?!\NWhere have you been, Sanji?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's nice to hear.\NBy the way, I think I can find the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Really?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But unfortunately,\Nwe can't just destroy it and get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be a much bigger task\Nthan we expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! We don't allow credit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody, catch that toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He ran away without paying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time!\NDoflamingo was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I just read the extra edition.\NHe sure fooled us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he gets Caesar back,\Nour entire plan ends in failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's destroy the factory and\Nput his nose out of joint!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway, you have to come meet us\Nat the Flower Field!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the name of that \Nplace so fairytale-ish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By the way, I can't reach Nami-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still see her as weak? \NShe's gonna be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook and Monster Chopper are with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is that?\N--{\i1}Huh? What's wrong?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.49,0:12:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Violet-{\i1}chan{\i0}, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a broadcast from the Colosseum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An unknown gladiator, Lucy, is pretty strong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He's quite a fighter!\N--Small but tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky, you won't believe \Nthis but, Luffy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:13:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's fighting in a competition now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.41,0:13:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you let him?!\NYou should've kept an eye on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're in no place to judge me!\NYou lost Zoro, didn't you?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Foot, I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My men are coming after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go to the \Nsecret factory, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NHere is a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's disguised as "Toy House."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this!\NIf you help me more, you're gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a funny man.\NIt doesn't make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the executives \Nalready know that I betrayed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Violet-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The western harbor! Meet me there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hide yourself there and \Nwait until I get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NThat's our rendezvous point!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:14:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will help you get away \Nfrom here at any price!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a good-for-nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to interrupt, you good-for-nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! Where did you come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Violet-{\i1}chan{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to beat them all up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing on the street like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you do it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do anything because they're \Nholding Kanjuro as a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to come with me, Sanji-{\i1}dono{\i0}!\NTo the place called Toy House!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where they are keeping \Nmy fellow samurai - Kanjuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI don't know where it is, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Entering from the general public,\Nno one really cared about him
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Lucy's doing really well!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, who's next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there is a strong \Ncontender left! Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bull from earlier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Do you wanna fight me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now Brutal Bull is facing \Nthe unstoppable Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brutal Bull fought death row prisoners\Nin this Colosseum the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will free the one of us who kills it\Nfrom death row.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a chance that doesn't come twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed so many tough \Nguys before I got caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kill this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He killed more than half of \Nthe prisoners in the fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NHe's certainly a killer bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Colosseum's Grim Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NBecause of his behavior, people call him Brutal Bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's charging at Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Lucy is just standing still!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he get paralyzed with fear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brutal Bull stabbed him with his horns...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.33,0:17:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lucy fended it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm over here! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Brutal Bull... s-stopped?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did Lucy do? What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NHe's riding on the Colosseum's Grim Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a man! Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.44,0:19:10.93,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,BACK IN GREEN BIT
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:17.57,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,UNDER THE FOREST
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:20.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE TONTATTA KINGDOM
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it shaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It must be Law and the others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I don't wanna die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--The hero is getting upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just kidding.\NThe truth is the shake was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...caused by my Haki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haki?! Isn't that the technique that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you used to kick 50 thousand villains' \Nasses on the Fish-Man Island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.83,0:19:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your energy can shake up this kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, please eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Fighting Fish.\NIt's big and a close relative of the goldfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A Fighting Fish?!\N--Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good!\NI didn't expect it to taste this good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes like the sea monster \Nthat I killed easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I thought,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they're the ones who \Ncaught the Fighting Fish.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How could they do that?\NThese Little People are that strong?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty big so it's several-months' worth of food\Nfor everyone in this kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usoland, you're a Big Human\Nso I guess you can eat a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffyland who belongs to my \Nfighting force - the Usolanders,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Ncan eat the whole fish with one bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's an Usoland?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. Doesn't that look familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's from the picture book \Nthat we read in Jaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NOLAND THE LIAR
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a statue of Mont Blanc Noland?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him, too, of course, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.64,0:21:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a Big Human botanist who came \Nvisit this kingdom 400 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, our ancestors \Nwere having a hard time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because the villainous Big Humans\Nwere messing up this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.02,0:21:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he fought with our ancestors\Nand led them to victory
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he became the legendary hero of\Nthe Tontatta Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.84,0:21:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Usoland said his name\Nand told us that he's one of his descendants,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was speechless!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Look at my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This chestnut-like head is the proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.84,0:21:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh yeah!\N--The chestnut-like head!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.67,0:21:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have any idea! I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.28,0:21:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a horrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.91,0:22:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were saved by it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat and get some gifts and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.69,0:22:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this must be destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To see them today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.09,0:22:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the day we vowed to fight \NDoflamingo and after 400 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a legendary hero came along again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usoland! After you finish eating,\Nlet's go to the Flower Field via underground passage!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.54,0:22:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At Dressrosa where we're gonna fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.65,0:22:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the commander and our fellow soldiers of\Nthe King Riku Army are expecting us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.59,0:22:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.72,0:22:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stand at the forefront and lead us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's destroy the Don Quixote Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.13,0:22:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.37,0:22:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Usoland, we're unbreakable!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:22:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.07,0:22:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.07,0:23:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usoland! Usoland! Usoland! Usoland! Usoland!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.15,0:23:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Usoland?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.05,0:23:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
